Andy Murray  of Britain has won the
third set of his U.S. Open semifinal against defending champion
 Rafael Nadal  of  Spain  and now trials two sets to one.  Nadal, the second seed, won the first two sets 6-4 and 6-2.
Murray, the fourth seed, took the third set 6-3.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
